shortName: THE NAGA GROUP AG NA O.N.
longBusinessSummary: The NAGA Group AG focuses on the development, marketing, and growth of disruptive applications for financial technology. Its products include NAGA Trader, the social network for traders; NAGA Brokers, a place where users can learn to trade through live and online events and Webinars; NAGA Virtual, a market place where gamers can monetize their game time; NAGA Wallet, an entry points to the world of cryptocurrencies; and NAGA Markets to trade with an EU licensed brokerage company. The company also offers NAGA Cybo, an AI robo-advisor to take care of investments; NAGA Academy for professional crypto, forex, and trading courses, seminars, and live Webinars; NAGA Exchange for cryptocurrencies exchange; NAGA Partners; NAGA Guard; and NAGA Card. The NAGA Group AG has various new products in the final stages of development, including NAGA Wealth, NAGA Local, and, NAGA Stocks. The company was founded in 2015 and is based in Hamburg, Germany.
